cascading.operation.aggregator
Class Last

java.lang.Object
  cascading.operation.BaseOperation<Tuple[]>
      cascading.operation.aggregator.ExtentBase
          cascading.operation.aggregator.Last
All Implemented Interfaces:
DeclaresResults, Aggregator<Tuple[]>, Operation<Tuple[]>, Serializable
public class Last
extends ExtentBase

Class Last is an Aggregator that returns the last Tuple encountered.

By default, it returns the last Tuple of Fields.ARGS found.

See Also:
